    <title>Motor Shield Reprogramming</title>
    <updated>2016-11-21T00:00:00+01:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;section id="motor-shield-reprogramming"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Create and flash new firmware for the WeMos D1 Mini Motor Shield.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/2343041479721475132.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-18439/images/2343041479721475132.jpg" src="projects/project-18439/images/2343041479721475132.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-none notranslate"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;We have pretty good information about the motor shield:
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The H-bridge is TB6612.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The microcontroller is STM32F030.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;We have a schematic: &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://www.wemos.cc/sites/default/files/2016-09/mini_motor.pdf"&gt;https://www.wemos.cc/sites/default/files/2016-09/mini_motor.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;We have the Arduino library for talking to it: &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/wemos/WEMOS_Motor_Shield_Arduino_Library"&gt;https://github.com/wemos/WEMOS_Motor_Shield_Arduino_Library&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;And, last but not least, we finally have the source code of the
original firmware: &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/wemos/Motor_Shield_Firmware"&gt;https://github.com/wemos/Motor_Shield_Firmware&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The shield has a serial interface for programming broken out, and that
chip is supposed to have a bootloader built-in, so hopefully we will
be able to just use stm32flash and an USB2TTL adapter to program it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is a nice dev environment template for this family of
microcontrollers: &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/szczys/stm32f0-discovery-basic-template"&gt;https://github.com/szczys/stm32f0-discovery-basic-template&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
